{
  "stem": "18575.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 218.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first school that my parents sent was a cheder, a Jewish religious school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't like the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall exactly the reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as far as I can recall, I didn't like the rigors of the teaching rabbis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I refused to attend that school after about a month or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my mother transferred me to a neighborhood public school, Polish public school, where I started my education.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Part of the education in a public school was-- in Poland was compulsory religious education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And being that they did not have a Jewish religious-- there were not that many Jewish schoolchildren, or the government didn't wanted to teach that-- I attended Catholic education, the catechism and all the other things, just as a [? sitting, ?] not that I took part in it the way the kids were.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, one of the teachers in the religious school was a very strict priest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I recall him very tall, in a black, long cassock to the floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he-- in the summertime just before vacation, it was very hot in Warsaw, he was always cold-- lock all the windows, and we could stifle there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was, I think, sadistic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to come to boys that did not answer correctly, pick them up by hair, on the side of his lock, right out of the seat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if you did any, any problem, or if you didn't go to mass on Sunday, he'll punish by putting a bag of dried beans he had in a corner of the classroom, and the kid had to kneel holding, 45 minutes of class, on the beans.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I can tell you that after you got up, you couldn't walk-- so that type of education.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
